  systemvalue : "QDSCJOBITV"
  description : "IBM i : Disconnected Job Time-Out Interval (QDSCJOBITV) - '<=120'"
  info        : "The Disconnected Job Time-Out Interval (QDSCJOBITV) system value determines if and when the system
ends a disconnected job. The interval is specified in minutes"
